title: In a fairytale Austrian town, locals protest against daily swarm of selfie-seeking tourists
description: The idyllic Alpine valley in which the Austrian town of Hallstatt rests looks like a fairytale come to life — so much so that visitors are struck by its similarity to the fictional icy kingdom of Arendelle in Disney's "Frozen."

title: North Korea fires cruise missiles into the sea as U.S.-South Korean military drills end
description: North Korea launched several cruise missiles into the sea Saturday, South Korea’s military said, in response to the U.S.-South Korea summer military drills.

title: Yevgeny Prigozhin's dead, but is Putin's authority strengthened after plane crash?
description: Wagner mercenary group chief Yevgeny Prigozhin’s mutiny and subsequent survival presented the most serious challenge to Russian President Vladimir Putin's two decades of iron rule.

title: Protesters in Syria demand end to Assad regime amid economic crisis
description: Hundreds of people took to the streets across Syria demanding President Bashar al-Assad to step down amid a crippling economic crisis in the country. NBC News’ Ellison Barber shares the latest.
